page.title: 02HOUSES-FLEETVILLE:ST.ALBANS
page.content: The majority of the houses within the area of Jennings Road, Brampton Road and Woodstock Road are Victorian or Edwardian but some date around 1920 to 1930. The area contains large detached Edwardian and Victorian houses priced in the region of Â£100,000 to Â£150,000. There are also large semi-detached properties around Â£70,000 and smaller terraced Victorian properties around Â£40,000 to Â£45,000. There are no council houses in the area. The estate agent who we spoke to, said that normally, he would expect at least ten to twelve houses to be on the market for sale at any one time.
